source: src/tests.rs
expression: render_command_help(&refs)
---
Start a new chunk within the current recording

Usage: bl record chunk start [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --name <name>    Name for the chunk
  -v, --verbose        Enable debug logging
      --title <title>  Title shown in trace viewer
      --headless       Hide browser window (visible by default)
      --json           Output as JSON
  -h, --help           Print help

Examples:
  bl record chunk start
  # Start a new chunk (for splitting long recordings)

  bl record chunk start --name "part2" --title "Checkout Flow"
